item.title: Compiler error need help fast
item.dc:creator: @str2own99 str2own99
item.description:
@str2own99 wrote:

[quote=“TOMSCAPE BETA, post:2, topic:365665”]Uh…I’ve never seen that one before. After doing some research I’ve narrowed it down to these two;

[ul][li]It was compiled with a different version of Java. You’re trying to run it in a differnet enviroment.[/li][/ul]

Sun Developer site:

Means the class file was compiled using java 1.5 and you are trying to run the class on a java 1.4 environment

[ul][li]It’s not there.[/li][/ul][/quote] oh i know now i changed it to 1.5.0_22
